OL,3,CManchester City considering legal
OL,4,Caction after Haaland claim
OL,6,FManchester City are considering legal
OL,7,Faction after a Real Madrid
OL,8,Fpresidential candidate claimed he
OL,9,Fwould sign Erling Haaland if elected.
OL,11,FSpanish businessman Enrique Riquelm
OL,12,Fpromoted his bid to take over as Real
OL,13,Fpresident in a TV appearance on 3 June
OL,14,F- holding a Real shirt with Haaland's
OL,15,Fname and number on the back.
OL,17,FHe said: "Haaland has a release clause
OL,18,Fand wants to join Real Madrid".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
