OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780600263
OL,3,CManchester City considering legal
OL,4,Caction after Haaland claim
OL,6,FThe claim was quickly shutdown by
OL,7,FHaaland's dad and agent, before a
OL,8,FManchester City spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"The stories which have emerged from
OL,10,FSpain regarding the future of Erling
OL,11,FHaaland are untrue.
OL,13,F"There is no chance of this happening
OL,14,Fand there is no contractual clause to
OL,15,Fenable it.
OL,17,F"We are considering legal action for
OL,18,Fthe use of our player image in this
OL,19,Fcontext."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
