OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780600263
OL,3,CManchester City considering legal
OL,4,Caction after Haaland claim
OL,6,FHaaland signed a new nine-and-a-half-
OL,7,Fyear contract at the club in January
OL,8,F2025, committing his future until the
OL,9,F2033-34 season.
OL,11,FThe Norwegian striker has been a
OL,12,Fprolific goalscorer for City since he
OL,13,Fjoined the club in 2022, and has won
OL,14,Ftwo Premier League titles with them.
OL,16,FIn the 2025-26 season, he was part of
OL,17,Ftheir Carabao Cup and FA Cup-winning
OL,18,Fteam and won the Premier League golden
OL,19,Fboot, finishing the campaign with 27
OL,20,Fgoals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
