OL,3,CManchester City considering legal
OL,4,Caction after Haaland claim
OL,6,FRiquelme also claimed he would sign
OL,7,FCity midfielder Rodri, who is under
OL,8,Fcontract at the club for the coming
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
